commentTextItems.html: short  ball on off and cut past point and Zimbabwe are winners again with 15 overs to spare and a whitewash of the series

commentPostTextItems.html: Zimbabwe were comfortable with the bat again despite early scalps by Kenya and they overhauled their target with ease in the end
Thank you for staying with us and looking forward to being with us in the near future
